        <h1>Top 3 Stock Market Strategies for 2025</h1>
        <p>The stock market is evolving rapidly, and successful traders must adapt to new trends. Here are three powerful strategies that can help investors maximize their profits in 2025.</p>

        <h2>1. Trend Following Strategy</h2>
        <p>This strategy involves identifying long-term trends and trading in the direction of momentum. By analyzing moving averages and breakout levels, traders can capture profitable price movements.</p>

        <h2>2. Value Investing</h2>
        <p>Inspired by Warren Buffett and Benjamin Graham, value investing focuses on buying undervalued stocks with strong fundamentals. Investors use financial ratios and intrinsic value calculations to find hidden gems.</p>

        <h2>3. Algorithmic Trading</h2>
        <p>With the rise of AI and automation, algo trading is becoming increasingly popular. Traders use bots and machine learning to execute high-speed trades based on real-time market data.</p>

